      <rules>
        <rule name="Get Tuff1" id="2808-f283-741a-ebbd" hidden="false">
          <description>Toughness: Snots start out quite squishy but soon 
toughen up. Once they gain enough experience to 
become Grots (21 experience points) they 
automatically gain 1 point of Toughness (in addition to 
any other advances). You do not need to update their 
cost when this happens</description>
        </rule>
