  <rules>
    <rule name="Never enuff ammo" id="00b4-4e09-17f4-abe3" hidden="false">
      <description>NEVER ENUFF AMMO
Without easy access to the Meks and other Orkish 
infrastructure, the revolushun is perpetually short of 
ammo and other supplies. This means a Rebel Grot 
Mob is more likely to run out of ammo at inconvenient 
times than other mobs. All members of a Rebel Grot 
Mob must take an Ammo Test on the roll of a natural 1 
or 6 to hit when shooting</description>
    </rule>
  </rules>
</catalogue>
